{"tid":2463934,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"考慮緊買唔買Monster hunter rise既人，可以入黎睇下","createTime":"2021-03-27T05:37:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T07:22:15.000Z","uid":342282,"like":59,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"b45b87bd129f053081540914bfeb3aae5e1b5965","tid":2463934,"uid":342282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T05:37:32.000Z","msg":"淨係略略玩過PSP年代既mon hunt ，同3ds 既mhxx<br />\n宜家只係去到村HR3 , 但已經覺得好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n優點 : <br />\n1) 易入手左好多，以前d村任打到媽媽聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但今集村任易左，岩曬一個人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，新手都唔洗怕，我條女未打過機都打到上HR2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , (去到集會所先真正開始黎料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n2) 有得騎狗，終於唔洗再慢慢行幅地圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,隻狗跑得好快下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每次任務都做快左好多~<br />\n3) 隻狗同貓貓會幫手打怪，唔洗驚打村任會悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ( 同埋隻狗好似幾勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n4) 翔蟲系統好正，會有少少好似spider man既感覺，配合埋拔刀斬怪會好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5) 以前一個地圖兩隻怪真係唔敢打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今集唔會再係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兩集怪你可以玩操龍 好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6) 霞龍同其他龍4月已經會出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n7)<del>見到有女仔名打集會所</del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n缺點 : <br />\n1) 隻game岩岩出，好多評測都未有，到底咩武器最正，咩裝備最好，大家都仲試緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新手自己摸索下<br />\n2)樓主自己都係新手，未必分析得好好，純粹用新手角度話俾1516既人聽，應唔應該買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfae5bd458397efc3bd70d14beb04193c46da020","tid":2463934,"uid":233316,"like":45,"dislike":2,"score":43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T05:38:38.000Z","msg":"買就買數位，買實體就食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f90eeab95ba5e398df1d58b7aa5ee1d32f36ea4","tid":2463934,"uid":66365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T05:39:33.000Z","msg":"pc 幾時有"},{"pid":"727ba83f1053f884a47bcb8d04e244dfb4540c34","tid":2463934,"uid":342282,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"1f90eeab95ba5e398df1d58b7aa5ee1d32f36ea4","tid":2463934,"uid":66365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T05:39:33.000Z","msg":"pc 幾時有"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T05:42:09.000Z","msg":"好似下年，但PC應該會少好多人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e52d2c97a922c21c51424d190e75d18bda42455","tid":2463934,"uid":94835,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T05:42:40.000Z","msg":"村BGM正到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時接左任都聽一陣先再出發"},{"pid":"40e5883222d553215a02998216cc52818a585435","tid":2463934,"uid":71342,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T05:44:43.000Z","msg":"主機有大貨未？"},{"pid":"9f239d76ab9dd83f49029d822f661c0de5224ee6","tid":2463934,"uid":261171,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T05:46:25.000Z","msg":"但第五果點真冇左mhw果隻生態系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇啦啦操第條龍去打人，操完又會乖乖地自己走開"},{"pid":"2a86079917513ffe4ef649cb600cfe549328487c","tid":2463934,"uid":22326,"like":1