faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5) 以前一個地圖兩隻怪真係唔敢打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今集唔會再係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兩集怪你可以玩操龍 好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6) 霞龍同其他龍4月已經會出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n7)<del>見到有女仔名打集會所</del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n缺點 : <br />\n1) 隻game岩岩出，好多評測都未有，到底咩武器最正，咩裝備最好，大家都仲試緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新手自己摸索下<br />\n2)樓主自己都係新手，未必分析得好好，純粹用新手角度話俾1516既人聽，應唔應該買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T06:40:22.000Z","msg":"7)見到有女仔名打集會所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我條仔唔使旨意買呢隻game<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b273f0b1957144538bdbf4d5545368de4e1163c","tid":2463934,"uid":12656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe9a2a7f72069c5b321457e125cd764761aab23a","tid":2463934,"uid":74970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e9ce849db5f78fd485195c68a1ad1688565a7e08","tid":2463934,"uid":71342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"792ade048721f4c61bd4155c089